  "description": {
    "de": "Mit diesem Schwert, das bei jungen Iops große Beliebtheit genießt, könnt ihr vielleicht eure Fähigkeiten unter Beweis stellen. Schließt es aber besser nicht allzu sehr ins Herz, denn das Schwert Ragen bleibt nie lange bei einem Besitzer.",
    "en": "Highly prized by young Iops, this sword will make a hero of you if you know how to handle it... However, be careful. Don't get too attached to it as it always falls down a well. Eventually, here or there, it'll fall down a well. Don't even try to avoid wells... you could be in a desert and THIS SWORD WOULD FALL DOWN A WELL. Got it?",
    "es": "Puede que esta espada muy codiciada entre los jóvenes yopukas te permita mostrar tu valía. Pero no te emociones demasiado con ella o acabarás un poco chiflado, cosa que no parece quitarles el sueño a los yopukas...",
    "fr": "Cette épée très prisée des jeunes Iops vous permettra peut-être de faire vos preuves. Mais attention, ne vous attachez pas à elle, car on finit toujours par perdre l'épée d'Alle.",
    "id": "995830",
    "pt": "Esta espada, muito valorizada por jovens Iops, pode ajudar você a demonstrar sua capacidade. Só não se apegue muito a ela, porque sempre se acaba perdendo a Espada Noza."
  },
